<HEADLINE>
`DON KOHLEONE' AND GERMANY FACE OFF 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By ROGER COHEN   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
