<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-31 10:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1580 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-GOP-TAXCUTS-REVIEW-2T     01-31 0788
