 &HT;    Best bests for shopping on the Web
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _
</P>
<P>
   www.outpost.com _ It's tough these days for an e-commerce site
to make hardened technophiles drool, but outpost.com has got the
goods _ computers, electronics, games, digital cameras, cool
massage and sleep accessories from Brookstone and more Palm
Pilot-esque travel toys than you can shake your mouse at. The
site's best feature is that outpost.com promises free next-day
delivery all year, all the time.
