created one of the most-publicized Web broadcasts in history (a
live lingerie Webcast that clogged up the Net last year), has an
extensive online shopping site _ you can see what's available in
your size, request a catalog, check out the spring preview or buy
gift certificates.
</P>
<P>
   MUST BUY: The ``Desire'' bra and bikini set, $38 and $20 each.
