<HEADLINE>
DAVOS: A GREAT GLOBAL ECONOMIC CONSPIRACY?  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (TIMELY for Davos summit!...Note 500-word trim; 1,125 uncut)   (This excellent ``separate-buy'' article is from the current (week
beginning 29 January 2000) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
