 (ATTN. EDITORS: FOR THOSE DESIRING A SHORTER VERSION, THIS ARTICLE
OFFERS THREE EDITOR-FRIENDLY OPTIONAL TRIMS, TOTALING 400 _ AT 700
(200 WORDS), 1,050 (100) AND 1,250 (100). TOTAL UNCUT IS 1,400.)  
  
