<HEADLINE>
CATHOLIC PRIESTS IN U.S. DYING OF AIDS IN SOARING NUMBERS  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Religion Editors...and Kansas City)   (This 525-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
