ATTN EDITORS:   NEW SCHEDLE FOR KEN HOOKER COLUMNS  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   Beginning the week of Feb. 6, Kenneth Hooker's personal finance
column, FINANCE-HOOKER (f), will begin moving on a new schedule,
related to a change in publication date for the column:
</P>
<P>
   --The Sunday column, previously sent in advance Friday, will
henceforth move Monday (Tuesday in the case of a Monday holiday.)
</P>
<P>
   -- The Monday column is moving to Wednesday publication in the
Globe; it will be sent to NYTNS clients Wednesday.
</P>
