   ECONOMY _ Congratulations, America, you've spent your way to
another important record: the longest economic expansion in U.S.
history. Tuesday is the first day of the 108th month of an
expansion that started in March 1991, as determined by the National
Bureau of Economic Research _ official keeper of business cycles.
The record is expected to lengthen, although the growth may slow
down a bit. (Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
