   COKE-DAFT _ ATLANTA _ Doug Daft says he can do without the
notoriety that has come with leading the world's largest soft drink
company. In a brief interview, Daft also says Coca-Cola remains
commited to being a corporate citizen in Atanta. He also talks
about his long days. (Unger, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
