<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-31 19:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2228 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-PINOCHET-CHILE-BOS &LR;      01-31 0783
