   SUPERBOWL_Ad samples.pdf -- 10p x 10 --
(BC-SUPERBOWL-AD-COLUMN-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   TAIWAN_Chip demand -- 28p x 3 1/2 -- (BC-TAIWAN-CHIPS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
